Program: Omnibus
Title: 50 Years of Language Services
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jgp
Last Broadcast Date: 31 December 1987
This programme celebrates 50 years of the BBC World Service language sections. It includes recollections from members of sections who tell how they came to Bush House, the home of World Service radio. Picture: BBC Bush House, London, Credit: Getty Images